    {\displaystyle {\mathcal {B}}\,(\cup )\,{\mathcal {F}}}
   is a greatest element (with respect to 
  
    
      
        ≤
      
    
    {\displaystyle \leq }
  ) of 
  
    
      
        
          S
        
        .
      
    
    {\displaystyle \mathbb {S} .}
  Let 
  
    
      
        ∅
        ≠
        
