              F
            
          
        
        
          
            F
          
        
        .
      
    
    {\displaystyle \cup \mathbb {F} =\bigcup _{{\mathcal {F}}\in \mathbb {F} }{\mathcal {F}}.}
   
The supremum or least upper bound of 
  
    
      
        
          F
        
        
           in 
        
        DualIdeals
        ⁡
        (
        X
        )
        ,
      
    
    {\displaystyle \mathbb {F} {\text{ in }}\operatorname {DualIdeals} (X),}
