If 
  
    
      
        ∪
        
          F
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle \cup \mathbb {F} }
   is not a filter subbase then the supremum of 
  
    
      
        
          F
        
        
           in 
        
        Filters
        ⁡
        (
        X
        )
      
    
