    {\displaystyle {\mathcal {B}}^{\uparrow X}=\{S\subseteq X:p\in S\}=\{\{p\}\cup T~:~T\subseteq \{1,2,3\}\}.}
   All three of 
  
    
      
        
          
            B
          
        
        ,
      
    
    {\displaystyle {\mathcal {B}},}
   the π–system 
  
    
      
        
          
            B
          
        
      
    
