            ↑
            X
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle p;{\mathcal {B}}^{\uparrow X}}
   is also an ultrafilter on 
  
    
      
        X
        .
      
    
    {\displaystyle X.}
  

Let 
  
    
      
        (
        X
        ,
        τ
        )
      
    
    {\displaystyle (X,\tau )}
   be a topological space, 
  
    
      
        
          
            B
          
        
        ⊆
        ℘
        (
