        )
        .
      
    
    {\displaystyle \Xi \subseteq \wp (Y).}
   Define

which contains the empty set if and only if 
  
    
      
        Ξ
      
    
    {\displaystyle \Xi }
   does.  It is possible for 
  
    
      
