    {\displaystyle \Xi }
   is downward closed (resp. closed under finite unions, an ideal) then this will also be true for 
  
    
      
        
          Ξ
          
            f
          
        
        .
      
    
    {\displaystyle \Xi _{f}.}
   Using the duality between ideals and dual ideals allows for a construction of the following filter.
     Suppose 
  
    
      
        
          
