    {\displaystyle h(M)\in I_{\geq i}.}
   
In particular, if 
  
    
      
        i
        :=
        
          (
          
            n
            +
            2
            ,
            
              B
              
                n
                +
                2
              
            
          
          )
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle i:=\left(n+2,B_{n+2}\right)}
   then 
  
    
      
        h
        (
        M
        )
        ≥
